data.description: Beautifully maintained 2 story townhome with 3 bedrooms up! Main bedroom has walk-in closet and private bath. Main level open floor plan featuring stainless steel kitchen with eat-in bar, separate dining area, and large airy living room with gas fireplace. 2nd level includes a great loft area and laundry. Across the street is a great park and green space. Move in ready!
